{"tid":1585613,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(賽後檢討) 我地缺既係 真.行動post","createTime":"2019-09-21T16:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T00:21:29.000Z","uid":160887,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d81954dc0889126959abbaf5fd136a699f298f42","tid":1585613,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T16:18:52.000Z","msg":"好多人成日出post話咩又冇行動post上熱門<br />\n其實唔係真<br />\n事實上都有唔少所謂&quot;行動post&quot;上熱門<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過係得張日程表／文宣圖</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地真正缺既係認真討論行動計劃既 真.行動post<br />\n例如呢類<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581744\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581744</a><br />\n推到21頁都係得100個正皮<br />\n<br />\n講番呢兩日既行動post<br />\n其實元朗站會停大家都諗到<br />\n但就係冇事先討論如果停轉去邊<br />\n又例如講左成個星期922搞黨鐵商場<br />\n但係都係冇熱門討論過實際上去邊個商場<br />\n個日程表重要係新城市(唔係黨鐵旗下)<br />\n又例如明知聽日好大機會機鐵會停到得番 香港站-機場<br />\n但係又係冇熱門post討論聽日係咪要迫爆香港站<br />\n陣間又一堆人衝入去機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">願榮光歸香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"5406f0f7eba78573e25e958410318c5968fa936d","tid":1585613,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T16:21:28.000Z","msg":"721 831 新屋嶺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c08ad2139c0c137e33fa1729b9f67035af154b","tid":1585613,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T16:22:02.000Z","msg":"721 831 新屋嶺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b2699973e77c422f1ac02a4f9b529921a78821","tid":1585613,"uid":37922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T16:22:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c98c8a781db8bfbc39cc49092d654b4f92653be","tid":1585613,"uid":248394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T16:22:57.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"902e3d0e7fb5b5e02d9178c2a72c49e2065f9427","tid":1585613,"uid":248394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci